{"tid":1719074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"敵進我退。教育局宣告停課至周日","createTime":"2019-11-14T04:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T05:21:27.000Z","uid":12152,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa58078dea5db0b403731e6fedd3c2fefa981290","tid":1719074,"uid":12152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"利申：唔係散水黨 只係分享d睇法<br />\n大家係咪唔記得6  7月點解我地咁機靈<br />\n因為be water呀。<br />\n依家班狗日日拉我地幾百位手足 真前線真係減少左好多 每一個人都好重要 唔好比班狗有機會再拉人<br />\n<br />\n依家個社會接近死亡狀態 18區佈哂狗 配合教育局停課<br />\n係街既狗就瘋狂搞年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議：前線手足休息，等教育局宣告復課果日再出動 ，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢行前我地就行後，目的無限期停課</span></span></strong>，<br />\n三罷入邊最容易係呢項了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1baeff15123b7f55d52a4f085878d1da1fb7c8","tid":1719074,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"只少都打埋聽日，完整一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1a73d0060308b125cbb6c936e495332965ef4c","tid":1719074,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線 ：向外國報告校園情況！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719066</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=f151ba48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"75c8320fe9c1cd3e3826f72a30b3c9cf11142b1c","tid":1719074,"u